snippet.title: 10-Minute Gameplay - SpongeBob SquarePants Featuring Nicktoons - Globs of Doom (Wii)
snippet.description:
A couple comments about this game.

1. Since when was the primary license SpongeBob? Weren't the other games called NickToons Unite!, Nicktoons: Battle for Volcano Island, and Nicktoons: Attack of the Toybots?

2. *sigh* Why did the Tak TV show have to change Tlaloc's name to Traloc? Did kids find it too hard to say?

3. WHERE THE HELL IS TIMMY TURNER IN THIS GAME???

4. I can no longer play as GIR. Kinda disappointing.

Just to make things clear... THIS GAME IS NOT BAD.
